title: Error When Converting To Codec
body:
Hello,

I've successfully converted a fake before but this time it is giving me slight trouble. I've seen a few issues posted that sound related but have never found a solution. Could it be a dataset issue?

I can convert seamlessly as long as I do not export with png's that contain alpha. Otherwise I get this error when converting raw as well.
